                <div class="static-img position-relative">
                  <div class="rounded-circle">
                    <picture>
                      <source srcset="images/description-img5-small.jpg, images/description-img5-small-2x.jpg 2x" media="(max-width: 767px)">
                      <source srcset="images/description-img5-large.jpg, images/description-img5-large-2x.jpg 2x">
                      <img src="images/description-img5-small.jpg" alt="image description">
                    </picture>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="small-img rounded-circle position-absolute">
                  <picture>
                    <source srcset="images/description-img6-small.jpg, images/description-img6-small-2x.jpg 2x" media="(max-width: 767px)">
                    <source srcset="images/description-img6-large.jpg, images/description-img6-large-2x.jpg 2x">
                    <img src="images/description-img6-small.jpg" alt="image description">
                  </picture>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="media-body text-center text-md-left order-md-1">
                <h2 class="title text-primary">Foodkit culture</h2>
                <p>At Foodkit, we believe in the importance of the  journey, not just reaching a destination. Our people are our greatest asset and we</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="media flex-column flex-md-row justify-content-md-between align-items-center w-100">
              <div class="img-holder d-flex mb-sm-3 mb-md-0 position-relative order-1 order-md-10">
                <picture>
                  <source srcset="images/description-img7-small.jpg, images/description-img7-small-2x.jpg 2x" media="(max-width: 767px)">
                  <source srcset="images/description-img7-large.jpg, images/description-img7-large-2x.jpg 2x">
                  <img src="images/description-img7-small.jpg" alt="image description">
                </picture>
              </div>
              <div class="media-body text-center text-md-left">
                <h2 class="title text-primary">Our mission</h2>
                <p>Our mission is simple. To build world class technology that changes an industry end to end and improves the lives of thousands of restaurant owners. We see technology as a great way to give advantage to restaurants  in a traditionally difficult industry.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
